'''''Étalon de Yennenga''''' ni igihembo gihabwa abantu b'icyubahiro bagize uruhare muri ecran ya silver ya [[Burkinabe]], gitangwa na Iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican ya Ouagadougou (FESPACO), mu rwego rwo gushimira Filime Nziza. Yatangiye bwa mbere mu 1972, ifatwa nkigihembo cyubahwa muri cinema ya [[Afurika|Afrika]]<ref>https://fr.africanews.com/2021/10/25/fespaco-2021-l-etalon-d-or-de-yennenga-pour-un-film-somalien/</ref><ref>https://www.voaafrique.com/a/fespaco-burkina-somalie-cinema-la-femme-du-fossoyeur-remporte-l-etalon-d-or-de-yennenga/6283265.html</ref>.

== Amateka ==
'Étalon de Yennenga' bisobanura Stallion ya Yennenga bivuga Umuganwakazi Yennenga, umugani washinze ubwami bwa Mossi, ubwoko bukuru muri [[Burukina Faso|Burkinafaso]].<ref>https://www.bbc.com/afrique/59068235</ref> Inkuru ya Yennenga yatangiriye mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 12 mu bwami bwa Dagomba bwa Mossi. Abasirikare b'umwami wa Dagomba, Nedega, bari intwari kandi hafi buri gihe batsindaga imbaraga zose. Umukobwa wa Nedega, Yennenga, wari umugore w'ifarashi, kandi yari umuhanga mu gukoresha amacumu, amacumu n'umuheto.<ref>https://abb-burkina.org/2017/03/01/les-trophees-detalon-de-yennenga-histoire-et-symbolisme/</ref><ref>https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Fespaco+2019+-+L%27etalon+de+Yennenga+%3A+des+origines+au+grand+prix+du...-a0673736016</ref> 

== Igihembo ==
Irasangiwe na [[Burukina Faso|Burkina Faso]] abakora amafilime azwi cyane, Idrissa Ouedraogo . Ouedraogo yatsindiye igihembo cya Yennenga mu 1991 kubera filime ''Tilai'' <ref>https://ifcinema.institutfrancais.com/fr/movie?id=5f1a07d8-5203-7838-5c30-ec08ac7f4834</ref>. Uwatsindiye iki gihembo ni Voltaïque Kollo Daniel Sanou mu 1983 hamwe na film ye ''Pawéogo'' (The Emigrant).<ref>https://www.voaafrique.com/a/burkina-faso-le-fespaco-%C3%A9pilogue--avec-le-sacre-de-l-etalon-d-or/6282140.html</ref> 

Muri 2005, FESPACO ya 19, ibihembo bibiri bishya byiswe "Stallion". Igikombe cya Stallion Award cyakozwe numucuzi wa Burkinabe Ali Nikiméa. Igihembo cya Yennenga gisanzwe gihinduka igihembo cyiza cya Yennenga, naho ibihembo bishya byitwa Yennenga Silver Standard na Yennenga Bronze Standard.<ref>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/somali-drama-wins-pan-african-film-festival-grand-prize-2021-10-23/</ref> 

